ormulae, as well as an interactive calculator of the significance of the\nrate of any of the neutrino sources relative to other sources taken as\nbackground.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Oct 2015 19:40:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Feb 2018 07:18:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 13 Jan 2021 02:46:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-14"}
