ve binomial point process. A scaling limit of these states as\n$\\kappa\\to\\infty$ gives the gamma random measure, depending on parameter $\\Re\nq$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Oct 2015 10:47:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2015 13:55:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 1 Jan 2016 11:35:11 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 3 Aug 2016 12:36:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-23"}
