expected, and have been interpreted in terms of final state effects such as\nhydrodynamic flow. These aspects make a study of charmed meson production in\np-Pb collisions as a function of the event multiplicity of great interest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Oct 2015 13:45:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-08"}
